♪ ♪

20:29.395 --> 20:32.137
♪<i> Come and sit</i> ♪

20:32.232 --> 20:36.049
♪<i> Around the tree</i> ♪

20:36.143 --> 20:39.478
♪<i> With me</i> ♪

20:39.630 --> 20:42.131
♪<i> Sometimes</i> ♪

20:42.300 --> 20:44.725
♪<i> Gifts are simply</i> ♪

20:44.819 --> 20:48.913
♪<i> Memories</i> ♪

20:49.064 --> 20:51.565
♪<i> Why don't you come</i> ♪

20:51.584 --> 20:54.326
